vements","count":1},{"word":"yes","count":1},{"word":"spacetrek","count":1},{"word":"collective","count":1},{"word":"annoying","count":1},{"word":"adults","count":1},{"word":"campus","count":1},{"word":"handle","count":1},{"word":"debate","count":1},{"word":"institute","count":1},{"word":"priority","count":1},{"word":"listen","count":1},{"word":"done","count":1},{"word":"business","count":1},{"word":"return","count":1},{"word":"mention","count":1},{"word":"suspect","count":1},{"word":"possession","count":1},{"word":"traces","count":1},{"word":"apologies","count":1},{"word":"responsible","count":1},{"word":"matters","count":1},{"word":"related","count":1},{"word":"tend","count":1},{"word":"cloud","count":1},{"word":"judgement","count":1},{"word":"incident","count":1},{"word":"warren","count":1},{"word":"upgraded","count":1},{"word":"safety","count":1},{"word":"protocols","count":1},{"word":"public","count":1},{"word":"lines","count":1},{"word":"overstepping","count":1},{"word":"peace","count":1},{"word":"offering","count":1},{"word":"i've","count":1},{"word":"granted","count":1},{"word":"full","count":1},{"word":"clearance","count":1},{"word":"passes","count":1},{"word":"starward","count":1},{"word":"riseway","count":1},{"word":"archive","count":1},{"word":"access","count":1},{"word":"use","count":1},{"word":"weaponry","count":1},{"word":"equipment","count":1},{"word":"personally","count":1},{"word":"apologize","count":1},{"word":"professor","count":1},{"word":"interrupting","count":1},{"word":"comms","count":1},{"word":"ensure","count":1},{"word":"next","count":1},{"word":"research","count":1},{"word":"grant","count":1},{"word":"substantially","count":1},{"word":"approved","count":1},{"word":"liking","count":1},{"word":"past","count":1},{"word":"lahai-roi","count":1},{"word":"kind","count":1},{"word":"connection","count":1},{"word":"described","count":1},{"word":"legend","count":1},{"word":"threat","count":1},{"word":"threnodian","count":1},{"word":"aleph-","count":1},{"word":"growing","count":1},{"word":"awakened","count":1},{"word":"returning","count":1},{"word":"trusted","count":1},{"word":"side","count":1},{"word":"humanity","count":1},{"word":"anything","count":1},{"word":"door","count":1},{"word":"open","count":1},{"word":"talk","count":1}],"lines":[{"text":"*************************************","quest_name":"All That Sunlight Touches","quest_id":189000000},{"text":"*************************************************************************","quest_name":"All That Sunlight Touches","quest_id":189000000},{"text":"**************************************************************************************************************************************************************","quest_name":"All That Sunlight Touches","quest_id":189000000},{"text":"************************************************************************","quest_name":"All That Sunlight Touches","quest_id":189000000},{"text":"********************","quest_name":"All That Sunlight Touches","quest_id":189000000},{"text":"**************************************************","quest_name":"All That Sunlight Touches","quest_id":189000000},{"text":"*************************************************************************************************************************************************************","quest_name":"All That Sunlight Touches","quest_id":189000000},{"text":"***********************************************","quest_name":"All That Sunlight Touches","quest_id":189000000},{"text":"************************************************************","quest_name":"All That Sunlight Touches","quest_id":189000000},{"text":"***********************************************************************************************************************************","quest_name":"All That Sunlight Touches","quest_id":189000000},{"text":"*****************************************************************************************************************************************************************","quest_name":"All That Sunlight Touches","quest_id":189000000},{"text":"******************************************************************************************************************************************************","quest_name":"All That Sunlight Touches","quest_id":189000000},{"text":"******************************************************************************************************************","quest_name":"All That Sunlight Touches","quest_id":189000000},{"text":"*************************************************************************************","quest_name":"All That Sunlight Touches","quest_id":189000000},{"text":"***********************************************************************************************************************","quest_name":"All That Sunlight Touches","quest_id":189000000},{"text":"******************************************************************************************************************","quest_name":"All That Sunlight Touches","quest_id":189000000},{"text":"*********************************************************************","quest_name":"All That Sunlight Touches","quest_id":189000000},{"text":"****************************************","quest_name":"All That Sunlight Touches","quest_id":189000000},{"text":"***********************","quest_name":"All That Sunlight Touches","quest_id":189000000},{"text":"*************************************************************************","quest_name":"All That Sunlight Touches","quest_id":189000000},{"text":"*********************************************************************************","quest_name":"All That Sunlight Touches","quest_id":189000000},{"text":"Now, we reach the second epoch of the Royan Trine Myth, the Sacred Reactor Epoch.","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"After Baldur, the Sun's incarnation, had sealed the foreign divinity Hvedrungr, the frostlands fell into an endless dream… Assistant Nivora, would you continue?","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"{PlayerName}, let's try to channel that enthusiasm into listening. Do come see me in my office after class, okay?","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"Assistant Nivora, if you would? Pick up from the Twilight Epoch's Unending Winter, please.","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"{PlayerName}. Something happened during class, didn't it?","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"…So a girl named Aemeath just got up and left the lecture hall?","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"Heh. I never expected to hear that name again. Certainly not like this.","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"Perhaps you've just had a run-in with a \"ghost\"?","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"After all... You were the only one who saw her.","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"Stay at Rabelle College long enough, and you'll eventually hear her name mentioned. Though it's a story from over a decade ago now.","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"Aemeath was a Synchronist. Brilliant. Popular. Professors had high hopes for her.","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"Then, during a piloting drill, she simply vanished.","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"She climbed into a simulator with the others. But when the cockpit reopened, hers was empty.","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"Intrigued? Want to go find her?","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"Of course. You're exactly the type to get pulled into Aemeath's story.","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"She saved you…? Heh, seems the mysteries around that girl are still multiplying.","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"To see someone who vanished years ago, presumed dead, lingering around the Academy… A figment of your imagination, or is there more to it? I'm very curious to find out.","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"She disappeared from the Synchrolink Training Grounds. The very cockpit she vanished from is still there.","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"The Academy turned it inside out at the time and found nothing. But if you're interested, go take a look.","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"I expect you'll dig up some new surprises for us.","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"My, my. Already caused a stir in the training grounds? Color me impressed.","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"I'll have people clean up the aftermath. You can carry on as you see fit.","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"You're a person of special interest. Of course we keep an eye on your movements.","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"Yes, \"we.\" The Spacetrek Collective. Think of us as the annoying adults on campus.","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"I'll handle the debate between the Institute and the Academy about the Core. This is a matter of priority. They'll listen to me.","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"But when you're done with your business, you will return the Core to the Exostrider, {PlayerName}.","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"You didn't mention it to Mornye, but I suspect... your possession of it traces back to Aemeath, doesn't it?","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"Heh, my apologies. As the one responsible for this Academy, matters related to the Exostrider tend to cloud my judgement.","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"After the incident with Warren, we upgraded safety protocols on public lines. No more overstepping.","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"Here's a peace offering. I've granted you full clearance: passes for the Starward Riseway, archive access, and use of Academy weaponry and equipment.","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"I'll also personally apologize to Professor Mornye for interrupting your comms and ensure her next research grant is... substantially approved.","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"How's that, {PlayerName}? More to your liking?","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"You should know. You have a past in Lahai-Roi, and you have some kind of connection with the Exostrider.","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"The Twilight Epoch, the Unending Winter described in Royan legend... the threat of the Threnodian Aleph-1 is growing. We need the Exostrider awakened. Returning that Reactor Core is the only way.","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"We've always trusted you to stand with us in this matter. To stand on the side of humanity.","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001},{"text":"You know where to find me if you need anything, {PlayerName}. And my door is always open if you just want to talk.","quest_name":"The Star That Voyages Far","quest_id":690000001}]}